Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value STATUS (up|down|administratively down)
Value PROTOCOL (up|down|administratively down)
Value PRIMARY_IP ((?:\d{1,3}\.){3}\d{1,3}|unassigned)
Value SECONDARY_IP ((?:\d{1,3}\.){3}\d{1,3}|unassigned)

Start
  ^\s*${INTERFACE}\s+${STATUS}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s+${PRIMARY_IP}\s+${SECONDARY_IP}\s*$$ -> Record
